Package: biotmle
Title: Targeted Learning for Biomarker Discovery with the Moderated T-Statistic
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Nima S. Hejazi <nhejazi@berkeley.edu> [aut, cre]",
    "Alan E. Hubbard <hubbard@berkeley.edu> [aut]",
    "Weixin Cai <wcai@berkeley.edu> [ctb]"))
Description: This package facilitates the discovery of biomarkers from Omics
    data based on the associations of potential biomarkers with exposure and
    outcome variables by implementing an estimation procedure that combines a
    generalization of the moderated t-statistic with asymptotically linear
    statistical parameters estimated via targeted minimum loss-based estimation
    (TMLE).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/nhejazi/biotmle
